Hi there! Let's get this sorted out. Are you using a specific tracking platform or service for your ClickBank conversions? This will help me provide more accurate instructions.

Thanks for letting me know you're using BeMob. To troubleshoot the issue with ClickBank conversions not showing, please follow these steps: 
1. Ensure that your ClickBank account is properly integrated with BeMob. Double-check the integration settings and make sure all necessary parameters are correctly configured.
2. Verify that your tracking links are set up correctly in BeMob and that they include the required ClickBank parameters.
3. Check if there are any filters or rules in BeMob that might be affecting the visibility of your conversions.
4. Review your ClickBank account to ensure that conversions are being tracked and reported accurately.
For detailed instructions on integrating BeMob with ClickBank, you can refer to this article: [How to integrate a Newsbreak Postback with CPV One](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/34188623183757-How-to-integrate-a-Newsbreak-Postback-with-CPV-One). If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
